How to play:

Each round is split between a 'morning' and 'night' phase. The game starts in the 'morning' phase, where all the users vote to eliminate who they believe the warewolf is. if the werewolf survives the 'morning' phase, the 'night' phase follows. In this phase, the werewolf may anonymously eliminate any other player we wishes. There will also be one wizard who can privately choose to protect one user from death the following night phase. This game will only end if all other users except the werewolf is eliminated, or if the werewolf gets eliminated.

Sign in or create an account to get started!
